      • navigateToCauser

        public void navigateToCauser()
        Description copied from interface: IMessageLabel
        Navigates to the control in which the faulty input was made and focus it. Is this Control placed on an not active respectively non visible IWidget, the corresponding widget will be activated and shown. Unless there is an parameter editor on the current active page, that handles the same parameter. Then this editor is given the focus.
        Specified by:
        navigateToCauser in interface IMessageLabel
